  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/coreaudiotypes\/kaudiochannellabel_centersurround\ncrawled: 2026-03-11T04:09:37Z\n---\n\n# kAudioChannelLabel_CenterSurround\n\n**Global Variable**\n\nCenter surround channel; or for WAVE (.wav) files, back center or rear surround.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nvar kAudioChannelLabel_CenterSurround: AudioChannelLabel { get }\n```\n\n## Labels\n\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_Ambisonic_W**: First order Ambisonic channel W.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_Ambisonic_X**: First order Ambisonic channel X.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_Ambisonic_Y**: First order Ambisonic channel Y.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_Ambisonic_Z**: First order Ambisonic channel Z.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_BeginReserved**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_BinauralLeft**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_BinauralRight**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_Center**: Center channel.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_CenterBottom**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_CenterSurroundDirect**: Back center, non diffuse channel.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_CenterTopFront**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_CenterTopMiddle**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_CenterTopRear**\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_ClickTrack**: Click track channel.\n- **kAudioChannelLabel_DialogCentricMix**\n\n",
